data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.100 set value "The snow crunches underfoot like whispered secrets."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.101 set value "I saw a Patron glowing gray through the blizzard. A Common one, they said."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.102 set value "Icicles hang from the eaves like frozen tears the sky forgot."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.103 set value "The northern lights paint the sky in colors I have no names for."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.104 set value "A Furia tore through here last week. The snow still hasn't settled."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.105 set value "Keep your fires burning. The cold is patient, but never kind."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.106 set value "They say the Heartstone pulses like a living thing in the dark."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.107 set value "The frozen river hums beneath the ice. Can you hear it?"
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.108 set value "Snowflakes never fall the same way twice. I have watched."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.109 set value "A Rare Patron with an aqua glow was spotted near the ridge."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.110 set value "Wolves follow me home sometimes. I leave the door open for them."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.111 set value "The frost etches patterns on my window. Each morning, a new world."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.112 set value "Dream Surges feel different in the cold. Sharper, somehow."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.113 set value "A warm hearth is worth more than emeralds out here."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.114 set value "The Codex speaks of things older than the ice itself."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.115 set value "I heard Mjolnir crackle once during a storm. Or maybe it was thunder."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.116 set value "Snow drifts can bury a village path in a single night."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.117 set value "The silence after snowfall is the closest thing to peace I know."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.118 set value "An Expeditionist passed through last moon. Brave soul, heading north."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.119 set value "The cold air carries sound for miles. Even the stars seem louder."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.120 set value "Structure crates sit frozen in the old ruins. Waiting."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.121 set value "Polar bears pace the ice like living monuments to patience."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.122 set value "A frozen lake is a mirror that shows you only winter."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.123 set value "The Wandering Trader braved the blizzard just to sell me coral."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.124 set value "You can hear the ice crack before it gives. Listen well."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.125 set value "They found the Frostbite Bow in a glacier, still cold to the touch."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.126 set value "The spruce trees bow under the weight of the snow like old friends."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.127 set value "A Greater Furia left claw marks in the blue ice. Three blocks deep."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.128 set value "The cold reveals what warmth lets us forget."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.129 set value "My companion fox curls by the fire each night. Good company."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.130 set value "Stars are clearer in the cold. As if the frost polishes them."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.131 set value "The Advantage Tree... I wonder what it looks like in person."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.132 set value "Snowflakes settle on the old rooftops like tiny blessings."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.133 set value "An Ornate Patron passed through once. Purple glow, terrifying grace."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.134 set value "A warm cup of stew can mend what the cold has broken."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.135 set value "The wind carries voices from the mountain. Or maybe just memories."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.136 set value "Strays walk the snow at night. Ice in their bones, arrows in hand."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.137 set value "I dream more vividly when the Dream Rate rises. Do you?"
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.138 set value "Frozen branches snap in the silence like small, sharp goodbyes."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.139 set value "The Miner profession must be brutal in permafrost like this."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.140 set value "Winter teaches you to love small things. A candle. A blanket."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.141 set value "Stormcaller belongs in a storm, not a chest. Let it sing."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.142 set value "When the aurora shines, the whole tundra holds its breath."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.143 set value "A fox left tracks around the village in a perfect circle."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.144 set value "Mob heads mounted on the wall keep the cold and the fear at bay."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.145 set value "The moon is brighter here. As if it shines just for the snow."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.146 set value "I heard the Blaze Core can warm a room without a fire."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.147 set value "Footprints vanish in fresh powder. Nothing stays forever."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.148 set value "The Guidestone glows faintly through the snowdrifts. A small mercy."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.149 set value "Ice caves hold a beauty so sharp it almost hurts to see."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.150 set value "An Uncommon Patron with a blue shimmer watched us from the treeline."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.151 set value "Long nights are for thinking. And wondering. And more thinking."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.152 set value "They say the Pebble of Dreams grants visions. I would ask for spring."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.153 set value "The cold wind is honest. It does not pretend to be gentle."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.154 set value "A Hunter left wolf pelts at our door. Kindness wrapped in leather."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.155 set value "Snowstorms erase the world and then return it, slightly changed."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.156 set value "The Harmonize melody sounds different when it echoes off ice."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.157 set value "Packed ice groans underfoot like a sleeping beast turning over."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.158 set value "A Minor Furia is still more chaos than I care to meet."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.159 set value "The winter sun barely rises, but when it does, everything glitters."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.160 set value "Warmth shared between strangers is the truest kind of wealth."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.161 set value "Weapon Mastery must help against those frozen undead out there."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.162 set value "The spruce forest whispers when the wind threads through its needles."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.163 set value "Earthshaker could split the glacier. I would rather it stayed whole."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.164 set value "A warm fire can turn a stranger into a friend in minutes."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.165 set value "Exquisite Patrons glow pink like a sunset on fresh snow. Beautiful and deadly."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.166 set value "Frozen rivers sing beneath their ice. A muffled, ancient song."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.167 set value "The Nymph profession feels at home in places like this, I think."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.168 set value "Blue ice is so clear you can see through it to forgotten things."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.169 set value "Every blizzard ends. That thought keeps me going."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.170 set value "The Ruin Watch ticks quietly. Even in the cold, time moves."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.171 set value "Wolves howl at the aurora. I think they are singing along."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.172 set value "The Bartender profession seems like a warm life. I envy that."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.173 set value "Snow muffles everything. Sometimes the quiet is a gift."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.174 set value "A Mythical Patron... gold glow, the mark of a falling star. Just stories."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.175 set value "The cold preserves things. Memories, too, if you let it."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.176 set value "Windrunner would carry you over these drifts like they were nothing."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.177 set value "My companion wolf sleeps at the foot of my bed. Best guard there is."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.178 set value "The northern sky holds more stars than I could count in a lifetime."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.179 set value "I heard an Artificer can craft wonders from scraps and will."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.180 set value "The frost on my window this morning looked like tiny fern leaves."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.181 set value "Structure crates in the frozen ruins refill. Patience rewards the cold."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.182 set value "A single candle in the window means someone is waiting for you."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.183 set value "The Tomb holds the fallen. Even the snow cannot reach them there."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.184 set value "Foxes leap headfirst into snowbanks to catch their prey. Such faith."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.185 set value "Dreams come easier in the cold. Something about the stillness."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.186 set value "They say a Wise Wanderer walked these ridges long before our village."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.187 set value "The moonlight on fresh snow is brighter than any lantern."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.188 set value "A Retired Adventurer settled near here. He stares at the mountains a lot."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.189 set value "Icicles grow like slow crystal thoughts hanging from the eaves."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.190 set value "Companion wolves sense danger long before we do. Trust them."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.191 set value "The Beekeeper must struggle here. Not many flowers in the frost."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.192 set value "Some nights the wind stops entirely. The silence is almost holy."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.193 set value "A Patron with the symbol of a star... Exquisite, they called it."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.194 set value "The cold teaches patience better than any master ever could."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.195 set value "Frostbite Bow frost spreads like a whisper across everything it touches."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.196 set value "I watch the snowfall for hours. Each flake a tiny, perfect life."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.197 set value "The Zookeeper would love the polar bears here. Gentle giants."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.198 set value "The winter wind carries the scent of pine and old promises."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.199 set value "Dream Surges in the snow feel like the world is waking beneath us."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.200 set value "An igloo half-buried in the drift. Someone lived there, once."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.201 set value "Keep your lantern lit. The dark and the cold are old allies."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.202 set value "A Standard Furia shattered the ice on the lake. We heard it for miles."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.203 set value "The cold night sky is so vast it makes you feel wonderfully small."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.204 set value "Wandering Traders never stay long here. Can you blame them?"
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.205 set value "Frost covers the world anew each dawn. A blank page, every morning."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.206 set value "The Codex says there are artifacts older than the glaciers."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.207 set value "A fur cloak is worth its weight in gold when the wind bites."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.208 set value "Patrons with the rare aqua glow leave footprints that shimmer."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.209 set value "The spruce trees are the only green for miles. I treasure them."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.210 set value "Frozen waterfalls hang in mid-fall, caught between moments forever."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.211 set value "The Advantage Tree must bloom somewhere warmer than here."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.212 set value "When the blizzard clears, the world looks newborn. Every time."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.213 set value "A stray shot an arrow that froze in midair. Or so they say."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.214 set value "Structure crates hide in frozen towers. Worth braving the cold."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.215 set value "The aurora reflects off the snow. We walk on a sky of color."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.216 set value "Mjolnir in a snowstorm would be something to behold."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.217 set value "I keep my fire burning all night. The darkness earns no welcome."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.218 set value "The Guidestone is a warm thought made solid. Bless whoever placed it."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.219 set value "Snow buries everything equally. Rich, poor, brave, afraid."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.220 set value "A Greater Furia in the snow is chaos wearing a white cloak."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.221 set value "The wolves and I have an understanding. We share the quiet."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.222 set value "Cold nights are for dreaming by the fire. And dream I do."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.223 set value "Mob heads on a fence post keep the strays thinking twice."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.224 set value "The frozen tundra stretches on. It is vast and it is honest."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.225 set value "An Expeditionist would thrive here. The north rewards the bold."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.226 set value "I found a flower frozen in the ice. Still perfectly pink."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.227 set value "The Blaze Core would be a treasure beyond words in this cold."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.228 set value "Snowflakes gather on my eyelashes. The world goes soft at the edges."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.229 set value "A Common Patron is still dangerous. Do not let the gray fool you."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.230 set value "The hearth fire pops and crackles. The oldest music there is."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.231 set value "Companion foxes are quick and clever in the snow. Born for it."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.232 set value "The ice remembers every footstep. Nothing is truly lost here."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.233 set value "Dream Rate rises and the snow itself seems to hum with energy."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.234 set value "I carved a tiny wolf from spruce wood. It guards my windowsill."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.235 set value "Weapon Mastery in the frozen wastes is a matter of survival."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.236 set value "The wind dies at dusk sometimes. The world holds perfectly still."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.237 set value "An Uncommon Patron watched from the hill. Blue glow against white snow."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.238 set value "Snowdrifts reshape the land overnight. Even the paths forget themselves."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.239 set value "The Pebble of Dreams must glow warmly. Everything precious does."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.240 set value "A polar bear walked through the village at dawn. No one moved."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.241 set value "Stormcaller and a blizzard together... I shudder to imagine it."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.242 set value "The long night ends. It always ends. Remember that."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.243 set value "Harmonize echoes beautifully off the frozen cliffs."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.244 set value "I leave breadcrumbs for the foxes. They leave silence in return."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.245 set value "A Patron marked with a gold star... Mythical. Surely just a legend."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.246 set value "The night sky here has more stars than the ground has snowflakes."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.247 set value "Windrunner boots in this snow would be a kindness to these old legs."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.248 set value "Every icicle is a tiny frozen waterfall. Beauty in stillness."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.249 set value "The Tomb markers stand even when everything else is buried in white."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.250 set value "I think the cold makes the heart grow fonder. Of everything."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.251 set value "A Furia with the minor mark still cracked the frozen earth."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.252 set value "Pine smoke on the wind means someone nearby is warm. That is enough."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.253 set value "The Ruin Watch reveals hidden things. Even things buried under snow."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.254 set value "Strays haunt the snowfields at night. Ice skeletons with cold aim."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.255 set value "The first snow of the season is always the most beautiful."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.256 set value "Earthshaker in frozen ground would split the world in two."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.257 set value "I wrap my hands around the cup and the whole world feels kinder."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.258 set value "The Artificer must know secrets for keeping warm. I would trade much."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.259 set value "Snow falls so gently. Hard to believe something so soft can bury you."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.260 set value "A structure crate glowed faintly through the frost. I dared not touch it."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.261 set value "The old watchtower on the ridge still stands. Barely."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.262 set value "The cold makes you honest with yourself. No room for pretending."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.263 set value "Ornate Patrons shimmer purple in the snowfall. Terribly beautiful."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.264 set value "A bowl of hot mushroom stew can save a life out here."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.265 set value "The Wise Wanderer told me the ice holds memories of ancient times."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.266 set value "Sometimes the snow glows faintly blue at night. I never found out why."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.267 set value "Foxes sleep in snowbanks with their tails over their noses. So wise."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.268 set value "The Codex must have a chapter on the frozen north. I hope."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.269 set value "Breath hangs in the air like a small ghost leaving your body."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.270 set value "Dream Surges make the northern lights dance twice as bright."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.271 set value "A warm hand offered in the cold is the bravest kind of love."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.272 set value "The Hunter profession suits the north. Patience and precision."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.273 set value "Frozen ruins hold secrets beneath ice that has not melted in ages."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.274 set value "I stack firewood like it is gold. Because out here, it is."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.275 set value "Companion wolves press against you in the cold. They know."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.276 set value "The tundra at dawn, touched by pink light, is the gentlest sight."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.277 set value "A Furia in the blizzard is the storm inside the storm."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.278 set value "The Guidestone hum is the only warm sound on the coldest nights."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.279 set value "I think the snow listens. It falls quieter when I whisper."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.280 set value "Frostbite Bow was made for a place like this. Cold finding cold."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.281 set value "The old paths beneath the snow lead to places we have forgotten."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.282 set value "A Rare Patron left tracks in the snow that glowed until morning."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.283 set value "This frozen silence is not emptiness. It is fullness, waiting."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.284 set value "The Wandering Trader brought cocoa beans once. Best week of my life."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.285 set value "Blue ice beneath the glacier looks like captured sky."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.286 set value "Mjolnir belongs to the storm. The storm belongs to the north."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.287 set value "The cold is not cruel. It simply is. We choose how to answer it."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.288 set value "Mob heads on the mantle remind me the wilderness has teeth."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.289 set value "A fox darted across the frozen lake without a single crack."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.290 set value "The Heartstone would glow so warmly here. A small sun for the snow."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.291 set value "Every winter I think this one will break me. Every spring I am wrong."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.292 set value "The Nymph would find beauty even in the bleakest snowdrift."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.293 set value "Ice crystals on the windowpane look like tiny frozen forests."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.294 set value "Structure crate loot gleams brighter against all this white."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.295 set value "I saw a stray dissolve at dawn. Even the cold has its mercies."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.296 set value "The Advantage Tree must bear fruit that tastes like possibility."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.297 set value "Snow on the spruce boughs looks like the trees are dreaming."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.298 set value "The Zookeeper tends life where it is fragile. A noble calling."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.299 set value "The last light of evening on the snowfield is pure gold."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.300 set value "Could you build us a proper chimney? The smoke has nowhere to go."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.301 set value "They say something ancient sleeps beneath the deepest glacier."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.302 set value "Build a covered walkway between the houses? The drifts are relentless."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.303 set value "The old watchtower saw armies march north. The snow swallowed them."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.304 set value "A stone fireplace, big enough to warm the whole room. Please."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.305 set value "The ice preserves bones from before our village was built."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.306 set value "Could you raise the fence line? Strays climb over when it drifts high."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.307 set value "The north remembers every traveler who did not return."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.308 set value "Build us a warm gathering hall. Somewhere to share stories."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.309 set value "Beneath the frozen lake, old structures rest in perfect stillness."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.310 set value "A lantern line along the main path would save lives in whiteouts."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.311 set value "The glacier has retreated three blocks since my grandfather's time."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.312 set value "We need a bell tower tall enough to cut through the storm."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.313 set value "Something glints deep in the ice. Metal, maybe. Or something older."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.314 set value "Build us a root cellar. The permafrost keeps things perfectly cold."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.315 set value "An old road lies under the snow. It goes somewhere we have forgotten."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.316 set value "A proper stable with insulated walls, for the animals. They deserve warmth."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.317 set value "The watchtowers on the northern ridge crumbled ages ago."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.318 set value "We need a bakery. The smell of warm bread is its own kind of fire."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.319 set value "There are carvings in the ice caves. Faces none of us recognize."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.320 set value "Build a greenhouse from glass panes? Even one flower would lift spirits."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.321 set value "The frozen shrine on the hilltop predates everything in the valley."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.322 set value "Could you add a roof to the well? It keeps freezing shut."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.323 set value "They say a whole city lies beneath the eastern glacier. Preserved."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.324 set value "Some benches by the central fire. A place to just... be together."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.325 set value "The old boundary stones poke through the snow. Marking what kingdom?"
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.326 set value "A cozy reading nook with wool carpets. Books and warmth, nothing more."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.327 set value "Whatever froze the river did it in an instant. The fish are still mid-swim."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.328 set value "Build an ice fishing hut on the lake. Quiet work for quiet minds."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.329 set value "The north remembers. The snow keeps its records in layers."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.330 set value "A lookout post to spot danger before the blizzard hides it."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.331 set value "Frozen armor pieces surface in the thaw. Whose were they?"
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.332 set value "Could you make a sauna? Heated stone, cedar walls, peace."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.333 set value "There is a sword frozen in the waterfall. No one can pull it free."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.334 set value "We need snow fences on the windward side. The drifts are winning."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.335 set value "The old maps show a tower that should be right beneath us."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.336 set value "Build us a storage cave. The cold keeps everything fresh forever."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.337 set value "Footprints appear in the snow some mornings. Always heading north."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.338 set value "A workshop for crafting by firelight. Warm hands make better things."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.339 set value "The ice shifts in spring and reveals walls that should not be there."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.340 set value "Could you insulate the roofs with packed snow? It works, strangely."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.341 set value "They dug too deep once looking for ore. They found carved stone instead."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.342 set value "A memorial stone for those the blizzards took. So we remember."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.343 set value "The permafrost holds things in perfect condition. Even secrets."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.344 set value "Build a tunnel between the main buildings. No more frostbite on errands."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.345 set value "Old watchtower foundations ring the valley. A garrison, once, maybe."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.346 set value "Some spruce trees along the path. Green is medicine for the eyes."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.347 set value "The deepest ice is blue. And the blue ice holds the oldest things."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.348 set value "A frost shrine for the spirits of the north. They deserve our thanks."
data modify storage eden:database dialogues.villager.snow.349 set value "Build something warm and lasting. That is all anyone here ever asks."
